data.description: Fully modernized DUPLEX w/ active tenants on both sides; unit A lease ending in less than 90 days. Enter a spacious and modern open concept, featuring a true chefs kitchen with high-end finishes, modern-style cabinets, granite counters, luxury fixtures, and backsplash. The property boasts generously sized bedrooms, a beautifully modernized bathroom, and a newly added laundry closet. Additional features include stainless steel appliances, updated heating/cooling systems, drywall and paint, siding, roofing, electrical and plumbing systems, gorgeous floors, completely updated bathrooms, and stylish finishes throughout. Exteriors also feature back decks and separate parking for each residence.
